---
title: Thai-Spiced Pork Schnitzel with Sesame Fries & Creamy Slaw
description: Spice up tonight’s schnitzel with our flavour-packed spice blend, coating the pork in a crunchy breadcrumb and cooking until it
shines golden brown. It’s not a schnitzel though without a side of fries. We’re baking them in a scattering of sesame seeds to go
with the spiced pork. Things are certainly getting fun.

